SELECT t.technique_name, COUNT(f.feedback_id) AS total_feedback, AVG(f.feedback_rating) AS avg_rating FROM Techniques t LEFT JOIN Feedback f ON t.technique_id = f.technique_id GROUP BY t.technique_name HAVING total_feedback > 5 ORDER BY avg_rating DESC;
